        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(1 comment)\n\nThe code in \"PropertyPasswordConfiguration.java\" is being repeated in traversal as well and probably other services (like Graphgraph) will need it too, wouldn't it be better to add  this shared functionality to the common project or somewhere where projects can reference it?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "d9bf891f6923cb5155ec066f904df3f12c4cad9e",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 75,
          "name": "Venkata Harish Kajur",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "vk250x@att.com",
          "username": "vk250x"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-09-24 15:14:42.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWhen you specify that the deployment is using generated certificates, then it will override those password properties and use the .password and .passphrases file. \nWe need to keep this until we are completely migrated to using aaf generated passwords.\nIts not obsolete because that isn't first delivered first of all and we need to be flexible so if that solution doesn't work out, we can switch easily.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
